<s> I think this is a CVS problem.  </s>
<s> The file really contains 0A 00 0A 00, and when you checked it out, the OAs were converted to OD OA. Presumably the files are not marked as binary in the repository, and you are checking them out on a MS Windows machine.  </s>
<s> I suspect this is the cause of the other problems you reported too.  </s>
<s> I seem to recall that this came up before, but no-one dared to run the command that would change every file in the repository to be marked as binary.  </s>
<s> -- Richard  </s>
